summary: On eve knowing which room Villanelle was in, she actually heard Villanelle giggle from the room!
question: On eve knowing which room Villanelle was in, she actually heard Villanelle giggle from the room!
answer:
Did she hear it? I couldn’t tell! I know Villanelle was doing a lot of heavy exhalations/sighing but I kept thinking: How thick are the door and the walls? Would you be able to pick up Villanelle making all those sounds through it?

In general, Eve is making a lot of correct leaps that is making her look not fully in possession of her wits to everyone else. She’s, uh, definitely eager. The contrast with her interest in Niko’s life is quite stark.

summary: Question: For those of you who do not have cable, how do you watch Killing Eve episodes live? I just found out my family is...
body:
Question: For those of you who do not have cable, how do you watch Killing Eve episodes live?

I just found out my family is canceling cable which means I won’t be able to watch it on TV anymore. I still want to support the show and be able to watch it live though. Are there any official sites that will premiere it live officially that I don’t need a cable provider to watch it with?

I only need this until the end of Season 2 so whatever costs me the least to be able to tune in would be preferable (meaning if I need to pay per month I would like it to be something I can immediately cancel after Killing Eve is done).

I really want to support this show as much as I can. It’s the only thing at the moment that is helping with my mental health by providing me something to look forward to each week.

Any advice would be greatly appreciated!!

summary:
Okay but can we talk about Eve's perspective on all that his happening?
After she stabbed Villanelle, all the contact she has...
body:
Okay but can we talk about Eve’s perspective on all that his happening?

After she stabbed Villanelle, all the contact she has had with her was when she listened to Villanelle screaming “EVE POLASTRI YOU PIECE OF SHIT” and the second time, the lipstick had a blade in it that cut her.

She must think Villanelle is pissed!!!

But then you look at it from Villanelle’s side and she was calling Eve because she was desperate and needed help and only screamed because she was frustrated that she wasn’t being understood and the lipstick was a weird romantic act on her part.

Best part is that even with all of this, Eve is into it 😂
